subSubSection.paragraph:
The type locality is a port on the Caspian shore, exhibiting strong freshwater influence from the Anzali wetlands inland, which may be drenched by the Caspian water during storms. Therefore, the salinity may vary yearly between 0 and 12.7 PSU (= Practical Salinity Units; Mirzajani pers. com.;
Mirzajani 2009
).

The presence of teeth on pleonite 1, 2 , 3 = Pl 1,2 , 3 resp. urosomites 1, 2 = Us 1,2 is indicated in brackets.
